This map is my first map. At least it is for Source. Please don't flame or start yelling at me because it sucks. Please keep those opinions to your self. If you got good opinions I will accept those. I will also accept constructive criticism.

There are only 8 spawns per team so there can only be 16 people max.
There are 8 Ak-47's.
There are 8 M4a1's.
There are 2 Awp's.

This Map was created by ZwinksTa.
I hope you like my map.
Opinions welcome unless its flaming.
Have fun. ^_^
